<br>
“Vendui again, my dears,” she whispers to those sisters assembled in the hall at this late hour, a wry smile coming to her painted lips.<br>
<br>
“I have come here at the request of Lady Nullo, as a result of our lovely meeting just a couple days back. Since my first journey here, several of your sisters have taken an interest in my sisterhood, and my interest has also been piqued in yours. I have hunted with some of you on several occasions, aided a couple through some troubling times, and started to form bonds, of a sort.”<br>
<br>
“Your Lady Nullo and I spoke of a potential gathering of our two sisterhoods, a meeting, if you will. That is why I have returned here at her request, to speak of such an event to perhaps learn from each other.”<br>
<br>
Lady Vivienne shifts and places her scythe at her feet, then locks her hands behind her. “I have come to you without my entourage, and stand before you weaponless as a sign of my intention.”<br>
<br>
Vivienne giggles, her crisp blue eyes becoming shiny, “of course, I still have my spells...” <p>What's the point of living if life is not spent dancing on the edge of the razor-blade?</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=20371A><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bcircleofsisters.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dalnin>Dalnin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder<br>Paddle Mistress</span><br>  Posts: 457<br> <font color=#660000>(7/15/02 12:30:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=238.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ..</span><hr size=1> *Dalnin turns looking at the dark elf her face twist in hatred,<br>
