As Dalnin springs towards Vivienne, a murmur of a chant interrupts the tense-quiet atmosphere of the room.  The green sparkling magic of a holding spell snakes itself around the monk's feet and dives into the floor.  It's not really enough to keep the much more experienced monk in one place, but it affords enough of a grip to at least give her pause for a moment.<br>
<br>
